std <- function(v) sqrt(mean((v-mean(v))**2))

xs <- (200:400)*0.01
sigma <- std(c(1,2,3))
belowSigma <- c()

for (x in xs) {
    newSigma <- std(c(1,2,3,x))
    if (newSigma < sigma) belowSigma <- c(belowSigma,x)
}

answer <- max(belowSigma)
cat(answer,sep='')
2.94
